name: Print any design on your Wallet
description:
Email us your design or photo to yo@printmyshizzle.com and we will do the rest! and email you back with a proof to check once you have placed your order

These printmyshizzle wallets are Thin, Lightweight, Strong, Recyclable, Tear and Water Resistant.

Every Wallet comes with two interior pockets for cash and receipts, two inward facing credit card pockets to keep your credit cards safe, and two quick access business card pockets for when you are on the go.

You can print any design on these wallets, from photos or custom designs you have, simply place your order and send us your artwork, we can print your custom printed wallets single sided and double sided 

Features:

    Tear resistant, water resistant, stain resistant
    2 pockets for cash and receipts
    2 outside pockets for business cards, gift cards, etc
    2 inner credit card pockets 
    Extremely slim, but expands with use
    Made from 25% recycled content, 100% recyclable
Dimensions: 20 x 8 cm (open)
